Package core.pubsub.publisher

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdvicePublisherActor
    Sends the advice notification written by doctor to the patient.
    HistoryPublisherActor
    Sends the patient's clinical history to the requester
    InfoPublisherActor
    Sends the personal information to the requester.
    LevelPublisherActor
    Sends the emergency (level 3) or alert (level 2) to the patient's doctors.
    MultiAdvicePublisherActor
    Sends to the requester all advices relative to a specific patient on a time range.
    MultiDrugPublisherActor
    Sends to the requester all drugs relative to a specific patient on a time range.
